parameters: Phew, you two gave me quite the fright...
I would've gotten a big one if you slaves escaped.
Hey, we're always on guard duty right?
And we're not allowed to touch the slaves?
There's no one around here but us, see?
Meaning, if we were to put our hands on 'em,
theoretically speaking, who can say that we did?
And as a precautionary measure, isn't there a need
to properly weaken them? I mean, who's to say they
won't just leg it first chance they get!
Well, then it can't be helped...!
I hope you're ready for what's comin'!!
Haah...it went died on its own...
I guess that little one got away...?
Ah well, slaves have got a curse put on them,
not like it can live a good life anyway...
